        <!-- LEFT / MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="col-lg-12 portfolio-info">
          <br>
          <h2 style="color:#12d640">AI-Powered Meeting Automation</h2>

          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Tech Stack</strong>:
              n8n, OpenAI / LLMs, Slack API, Notion API, JavaScript, Prompt Engineering
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Project Type</strong>:
              Enterprise Workflow Automation (Case Study)
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            Designed and implemented an end-to-end AI-powered meeting automation system that converts raw,
            unstructured meeting notes into structured summaries, decisions, and actionable tasks.
          </p>

          <p>
            The workflow uses <strong>n8n</strong> as the orchestration layer, integrates
            <strong>LLM-based extraction</strong> for meeting intelligence, enables
            <strong>Slack-based organizer review and approval</strong>, and publishes
            approved content into a <strong>Notion knowledge base</strong>.
          </p>

          <p>
            The system also expands approved action items into individual tasks and automatically notifies
            assignees via Slack, eliminating manual follow-ups and improving accountability.
          </p>

          <h5 style="color:#12d640; margin-top:30px;">Key Capabilities</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Automated ingestion and grouping of raw meeting notes</li>
            <li>LLM-based extraction of summaries, decisions, and action items</li>
            <li>Slack-based approval workflow for meeting organizers</li>
            <li>Staging → final promotion to a centralized Notion knowledge base</li>
            <li>Automatic creation and distribution of action items to assignees</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 style="color:#12d640; margin-top:30px;">Impact</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Reduced manual meeting documentation effort by ~80–90%</li>
            <li>Improved consistency and quality of meeting records</li>
            <li>Increased follow-through on action items via automated reminders</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 style="color:#12d640; margin-top:30px;">Architecture Overview</h5>
          <p>
            Below is a high-level workflow diagram illustrating the system design
            (simplified for confidentiality).
          </p>

